casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Zapata et al., Appellants.

[Cite as State v. Zapata (1986), 25 Ohio St. 3d 66.]

(No. 85-1940 Decided July 16, 1986.) M. Scott Ramey, for appellee. Lydy, Moan & Douglas and James E. Moan, for appellants.

*67This cause (consisting of case Nos. L-85-117 through L-85-123), certified by the court of appeals as being in conflict with State v. Schell (1984), 13 Ohio App. 3d 313, is affirmed on authority of State v. Dickerson (1986), 25 Ohio St. 3d 64, decided this date.

Celebrezze, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, C. Brown, Douglas and Wright, JJ., concur.
